### âœ… Step 2: Download a Good Config File
A **Sysmon config** tells it **what to log** and **what to ignore**.

Use this trusted config:
ğŸ“¥ [SwiftOnSecurity Config on GitHub](https://github.com/SwiftOnSecurity/sysmon-config)

